main event: Multiple photographs of an unidentified flying object (UFO) captured in the sky above various locations in Ontario, Canada in 1967.
interesting points: The UFOs observed were consistently described as dark and disc-shaped,Several photographs depict the UFOs over residential neighborhoods,The reports appear to come from the Foreign Technology Division, indicating a government interest in the phenomena,The photographs vary in clarity, suggesting the objects may have been moving quickly,The sightings were part of documentation likely related to Project Blue Book.
